    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Valerius <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Gal</abbr><ex>eria</ex></expan> Valerianus Cisimbrensis IIvir <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>pontif</abbr><ex>ex</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>perp</abbr><ex>etuus</ex></expan> forum aedes quinque signa <expan><abbr>deor</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>quinque statuas suas sua impensa dedit donavit <lb n="4"/>Flavia Valeriana neptis heres epulo dato dedicavit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Das Stück ist nicht mehr auffindbar. Valerius Valerianus ist der Mann von Valeria Acte (CIL II² 5, 296).</p>
            </div>
